DDUH Recruitment 2025 - Walk-in-Interview for 12 Senior Resident Posts
Prasanna / All Government Jobs / Jul 30, 2025, 12:32 IST
 Greater Hyderabad Municipal Corporation
 12 Jobs |  Posted On : 30-Jul-2025 |  Delhi |  Salary : 67,700 to 208,700




FOLLOW

The Deen Dayal Upadhyay Hospital (DDUH) has announced the official notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for 12 Senior Resident Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the MBBS, MD/ MS, DNB, and Post-Graduation can apply for the DDUH Recruitment 2025. Here we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested and eligible candidates can apply on or before the last date of application. For more details, visit the official website.




If you are looking for more, here is a list of Government Jobs in 2025 that you can all apply for. Use this link for more jobs in Delhi.

DDUH Recruitment 2025 - Eligibility Criteria
Name of the Posts	No.of Vacancies	Qualification
Senior Resident 	12	MBBS, MD/ MS, DNB, Post Graduation

Age Limit for the DDUH Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Age Limit: 21 years.
The Maximum Age Limit: 45 years.

Age Relaxation

OBC Candidates: 3 Years
SC/ ST Candidates: 5 Years

Selection Process for the DDUH Recruitment 2025

Interview

Salary Structure for the DDUH Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Salary: Rs. 67,700 /- per month.
The Maximum Salary: Rs. 2,08,700 /- per month.

Application fee for the DDUH Recruitment 2025

There is no application fee.
How to Apply for the DDUH Recruitment 2025
Visit the official website.
Go to the Recruitment or career page.
Check for the Senior Resident Notification 2025.
Read the notification carefully.
Check the eligibility criteria.
If you meet the eligibility criteria.
Download the application form.
Fill out the application form carefully.
Then, attend the walk-in interview along with the documents required to the address given below.

Venue

The Seminar Hall (Ground Floor), Doctor’s Hostel, DDUH

Important Dates

Starting Date of Application	25-07-2025
Date of Walk-in-Interview	05-08-2025 to 19-08-2025
